	lies from start to finish as they transition from their homes to retiremen
	t communities. Nicole Bates\, Relocation Consultant at Hansen Bros. Moving
	 & Storage and HB Move Management\, has assisted thousands of clients with
	 their moves and specializes in working with clients downsizing from a lon
	g-time home to a smaller living space. Complimentary valet parking will be
	 provided for your convenience.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/d
	etails/living-large-with-less-stuff/18305951/2026-03-26T00
